---

let teacherName = '...';
---

<div
	class="bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-100 to-slate-200 dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-slate-800 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-20 p-4 lg:p-16 shadow-xl shadow-slate-200 dark:shadow-slate-900"
>
	<header
		class="p-8 flex justify-center items-center flex-wrap flex-col w-full mt-16"
	>
	<div class="flex justify-center w-full ">
		<img src='/static/images/felogo_rework.png' alt="FE Logo" class="w-48 h-48 hidden dark:block" />
		<img src='/static/images/felogo_rework.png' alt="FE Logo" class="w-48 h-48 invert  dark:hidden" />

	  </div>

		<div class="format dark:format-invert lg:format-lg mt-32">
			<p class="text-4xl lg:text-8xl dark:text-slate-200 text-slate-600 leading-tight text-center">
				Welcome, <a
					id="teacherName"
					class="font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-400 to-violet-800 dark:from-emerald-500 dark:to-purple-700 no-underline animate-pulse"
					>{teacherName}</a>
				<br />
			</p>

			<div class="format dark:format-invert lg:format-lg mt-32">
				<p class="text-xl lg:text-xl dark:text-slate-200 text-slate-600 leading-tight text-center">
					Step into an era where AI empowers your teaching experience. With Futurist-Edu, transform how you educate, crafting courses effortlessly with AI-generated content
					 that adapts to each student's needs. Elevate your teaching, track progress in real-time, and inspire success in every learner. Your journey to redefine education
					  begins now – one innovative lesson at a time!" <br> <br> Where <a
						rel="noopener nofollow"
						class="font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-400 to-violet-800 dark:from-emerald-500 dark:to-purple-700 no-underline"
						>Teaching</a>
						Meets
						<a
						rel="noopener nofollow"
						class="font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-400 to-violet-800 dark:from-emerald-500 dark:to-purple-700 no-underline"
						>Technology</a>
						– Together, we're shaping the future of learning.

				</p>
		
			<div class="flex justify-center space-x-5 w-full">
				<a
					href="/teacher/CourseSelector"
					type="button"
					class="text-blue-800 hover:text-white border hover:bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-400 to-violet-800 dark:from-emerald-500 dark:to-purple-700 border-blue-700 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5 text-center mr-2 mb-2 dark:border-blue-500 dark:text-blue-100 dark:hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-blue-600 dark:focus:ring-blue-800"
					>Go to your Courses</a>
					<a
					href="/teacher/upload"
					type="button"
					class="text-blue-800 hover:text-white border hover:bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-400 to-violet-800 dark:from-emerald-500 dark:to-purple-700 border-blue-700 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5 text-center mr-2 mb-2 dark:border-blue-500 dark:text-blue-100 dark:hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-blue-600 dark:focus:ring-blue-800"
					>Create Questions</a>
					
			</div>
		</div>
	</header>
</div>

<script>
	import { fetchTeacherName } from './TeacherReadMe.client'; 
	
	if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
		fetchTeacherName(24).then(name => { //Currently Hardcoded, as Login is not enabled
			const teacherNameElement = document.getElementById('teacherName');
			if (teacherNameElement) {
				teacherNameElement.textContent = name;
				teacherNameElement.classList.remove('animate-pulse');
			}
		});
	}
	</script>

<style>
	/* Override in Markdown H1 title */
	.readme :global(h1:nth-of-type(2)) {
		display: none;
	}

	.svg-inline :global(svg) {
		height: 100%;
		width: 100%;
	}
	
</style>

